<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6" align="center">
    <B><H2>Import:</H2></B>
    <div class="col-md-12" align="left">
      <P>Students have three values: id_number, first_name & last name. All values are required for import. Your .csv should have three populated columns with the first row of each column being one of the three values. Example:<br>
      <br>
      <center>
        <%= image_tag "excel.png" %>
        <br>
        <br>
        <p class="text-danger">
          <b>ALERT:</b> Your import must contain a complete roster.<br>
          All students not included in the csv will be disabled.
        </p>
        <br>
        <%= form_tag import_submit_path, multipart: true do %>
          <div class="col-md-12" align="center">
            <%= file_field_tag :file, class: "btn btn-success btn-file" %><br>
            <%= submit_tag "Import", class: "btn btn-success" %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </center>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>